                    <h3>Article Spotlight: The Power of HTML5</h3>
                    <p>The **&lt;article&gt;** tag is used for independent, self-contained content, like a blog post or a news item. HTML5 introduced many tags to make web structure clearer for browsers and search engines.</p>
                    
                    <aside>
                        <h4>Quick Note (Sidebar Info)</h4>
                        <p>This information, enclosed in the **&lt;aside&gt;** tag, is related to the main content but stands apart, like a sidebar or a pull quote.</p>
                    </aside>

